parameters.name: AppIds
parameters.description: The IDs of the jobs that are submitted to YARN.

parameters.name: EndRange
parameters.description: The range of end time. You can filter jobs whose end time falls within the specified time range.

parameters.name: MaxResults
parameters.description: The maximum number of entries to return on each page.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description: The pagination token that is used in the request to retrieve a new page of results.

parameters.name: OrderBy
parameters.description:
The field that you use to sort the query results. Valid values:

*   vcoreSeconds: the aggregated number of vCPUs that are allocated to the job multiplied by the number of seconds the job has been running
*   memSeconds: the aggregated amount of memory that is allocated to the job multiplied by the number of seconds the job has been running

parameters.name: OrderType
parameters.description:
The order in which you want to sort the query results. Valid values:

*   ASC: the ascending order
*   DESC: the descending order

parameters.name: Queues
parameters.description: The YARN queues to which the jobs are submitted.

parameters.name: StartRange
parameters.description: The range of start time. You can filter jobs whose start time falls within the specified time range.

parameters.name: Types
parameters.description: The YARN engines to which the jobs are submitted.

parameters.name: Users
parameters.description: The users who submit the jobs.
